Introduction for Hara Ceylon Tea

Discover the pure essence of Sri Lanka with Hara Ceylon Tea—a celebration of tradition, craftsmanship, and natural richness. Handpicked from the lush highlands of Ceylon, our teas are carefully curated to bring you unmatched freshness, aroma, and character in every sip.
From vibrant green teas to bold black varieties, Hara Ceylon Tea delivers a refined taste that honors centuries of tea-making heritage. Experience the true art of Ceylon tea—naturally authentic, ethically sourced, and crafted for moments of pure indulgence.

Awaken your senses with Hara Ceylon Coffee, grown in the fertile soils and misty mountain slopes of Sri Lanka’s renowned coffee regions. Our beans are expertly harvested and slow-roasted to perfection, unveiling deep, smooth flavors with every cup.
Hara Ceylon Coffee offers a distinctive profile that blends tradition with modern craftsmanship. Taste the harmony of aroma, flavor, and freshness that defines true Ceylon coffee.

About Us

Hara Ceylon Ltd is a proudly Sri Lankan company dedicated to delivering the finest natural products sourced from the fertile soils and rich heritage of Ceylon. We specialize in ethically produced, high-quality goods that reflect our commitment to authenticity, sustainability, and excellence.
With a passion for innovation and a deep respect for tradition, Hara Ceylon Ltd connects the world with the purity and richness of Sri Lanka’s natural resources.


Why Choose Us
	•	Unmatched Quality: Every product is carefully selected, processed, and packaged to meet the highest international standards.
	•	Ethically Sourced: We support local farming communities, ensuring fair practices and sustainable land use.
	•	Pure & Natural: Our products are free from harmful chemicals, additives, and artificial enhancements.
	•	Reliable Service: With a strong supply chain and dedicated customer support, we ensure consistency, transparency, and timely delivery.
	


Vision

To become a globally recognized leader in premium Sri Lankan natural products, empowering communities, protecting the environment, and enriching lives around the world through sustainable excellence.



Mission
	•	To deliver exceptional, ethically sourced Ceylon products that embody purity, quality, and authenticity.
	•	To cultivate long-term partnerships with farmers, customers, and stakeholders through transparency and trust.
	•	To innovate sustainably, ensuring our practices protect Sri Lanka’s natural heritage for future generations.